Reconstructed diary of a Menesian priestess
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Tarik is Channan's best friend. He and my son learned walking together. With age came rivalry. I see how both look at Saikka. Tarik is a strong boy but he is no match for my son. And Saikka feels the same way.


The tournament will start soon. As every year, townspeople are agitated and excited. The boys exercise, eager to receive the honor from the Goddess. 


I have to act.
